TextEng: I am not Karlat.
Me not Karlat.
What manner of demon are you?
What demon kind is you?
Foul beast! Belay your tempting tongue.
Foul thing! Me not listen to your words!
Text: 더러운 놈! 나 네 말 안 들어!

TextEng: I tell you I am not Karlat!
But me not Karlat!
Divination?
Divi-whasis?
I will not speak, demon! I will destroy you!
Text: 악마한테 말 안 해! 널 죽여버릴 거야!

TextEng: Me say nothing, demon! Me destroy you!
Text: 나 말 안 해, 악마! 나 너 죽여!

TextEng: Tell me of my past. What I did to get here.
Text: 내 과거에 대해 말해줘. 내가 뭘 해서 여기까지 왔는지.

TextEng: Talk of past for me.
What could go wrong in my transformation?
Text: 변신에 무슨 문제가 생길 수 있어?

TextEng: What might go bad when me change?
Text: 나 변할 때 뭐가 잘못될 수 있어?

TextEng: What happens if I become a lich?
What happens if me become lich?
Goodbye.
What do you know of the Cult of the Old Ones?
What you know of Old One cult?
Text: 너 구자들 사교에 대해 뭘 알아?

TextEng: Goodbye.
